<template>
    <section>
        <input type="text" v-model="agentMasterKey">
        <button @click="getAgent">
            Get Agent
        </button>
    </section>
</template>

<script>

import axios from "axios";
export default {
    data() {
        return {
            agentMasterKey: '',
            image_cma_pdf_logo_header: '',
            image_cma_pdf_logo_header_light: '',
            background_color_primary: '',
            background_color_secondary: ''
        }
    },
    computed:{
        style: function() {
            // font-family: this.background_color_secondary
        }
    },
    methods: {
        getAgent() {
            $.ajax({
                url: `/api/get_agent/${this.agentMasterKey}`,
                method: 'GET',
                success: function(res) {
                    console.log(res)
                }
            })
        }
    }
}
</script>
